title: Etta James & Eddie Cleanhead Vinson - The Late Show - Blues
description:
Etta James & Eddie 'Cleanhead' Vinson - The Late Show: Blues in the Night Volume Two
Label: Fantasy Records
Format: CD, Album
Country: US
Released: Oct 25, 1990
Recorded live at Marla's Memory Lane Supper Club, Los Angeles, California on May 30 & 31, 1986



Tracklist:

01	Cleanhead Blues
02	Old Maid Boogie
03	Home Boy
04	Cherry Red
05	Baby, What You Want Me To Do
06	Sweet Little Angel
07	I'd Rather Go Blind
08	Teach Me Tonight
09	Only Women Bleed
10	He's Got the Whole World in His Hands



Lineup:

      Etta James - vocals
      Eddie "Cleanhead" Vinson - vocals and alto sax
      Red Holloway - alto, tenor and baritone saxes
      Jack McDuff- Hammond B-3
      Shuggie Otis - guitar
      Richard Reid - acoustic & electric bass
      Paul Humphrey - drums
